WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.860
Today on this 2006 Pontiac Montana we are
going to be installing wiring harness part

00:00:03.860 --> 00:00:04.860
number 118396.

00:00:04.860 --> 00:00:09.560
We are at the rear of the vehicle, with the
cargo door open, and we want to go ahead and

00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:12.542
locate the port that our wiring harness is
going to be plugging into.

00:00:12.542 --> 00:00:15.300
The ports are located directly behind the
taillight on both the driver and passenger

00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:16.300
side.

00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:18.880
So the first thing that we want to go ahead
and do is remove both taillight assemblies.

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:22.880
Holding the taillight in place on the inboard
side are two torque headed bolts.

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:35.230
We need to go ahead and take those out.

00:00:35.230 --> 00:00:40.050
0:38
With the taillight removed, you can look at

00:00:40.050 --> 00:00:41.200
the back side here.

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:44.289
This main port is the port we are going to
be using to plug our wiring harness into.

00:00:44.289 --> 00:00:46.210
So, I am just going to go ahead and separate
the two pieces.

00:00:46.210 --> 00:00:47.560
There is a tab up top.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:51.190
You just want to press that in and pull away
from the taillight.

00:00:51.190 --> 00:00:53.199
And that separates them.

00:00:53.199 --> 00:00:56.070
Over here on our driver side, we are going
to plug in our ports that have the yellow

00:00:56.070 --> 00:00:57.770
and brown wires in them.

00:00:57.770 --> 00:01:02.170
These are basically just going to plug inline
in that disconnect point we just made.

00:01:02.170 --> 00:01:04.470
I am going to leave the taillight off for
the time being.

00:01:04.470 --> 00:01:08.119
What we are going to do is take the passenger
side connector, along with the 4-pole, and

00:01:08.119 --> 00:01:11.070
we are going to feed them down through the
opening in between the body and the bumper

00:01:11.070 --> 00:02:54.430
1:15

